# cars

**Instance Property**

An array of the user’s electric vehicles.

## Declaration

```swift
var cars: [INCar]? { get set }
```

## Discussion

Set this property to an array of [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INCar] objects that represents the user’s electric vehicles. Maps requires these vehicles to respond to [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INGetCarPowerLevelStatusIntent] requests so that it can use them during route planning and navigation.

## Providing a List of Cars

- **INCar**: A specific electric vehicle that Maps uses during route planning and navigation.
